John Longden https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Longden 0 John Longden (11 November 1900 – 26 May 1971) was a West Indian-born English film actor. He appeared in 84 films between 1926 and 1964, including five films directed by Alfred Hitchcock. John_Longden ( 11_November_1900 – 26_May_1971 ) was a_West_Indian-born_English_film_actor .
